Responsibilities : 
Implementing key TOSCA features in Automation assignment like Requirement Mapping, Test Case Design, Test Case, Test Execution and Modules 
Identify and propose value adding Test Automation solutions appropriate for each Business area, domain, platform or product 
Development of test automation framework , testing processes and procedures using TOSCA Tool 
Writing TQLs (Tosca Query Language) for different tasks as per scope of work 
Must have worked as a TOSCA Architect of minimum 2+ years, while overall Test Automation Experience (using Selenium, Java, UFT, QTP, Worksoft, Python, R, C#) should be at least 12+ years 
Strong understanding of CI / CD Integration, including integrating TOSCA automation in DevOps pipeline 
Experience in automating SAP Business Scenarios / Platforms such as Sterling Ecommerce, Workday or other cloud based platform solutions 
Good knowledge in Automation Testing and can carry out Automation domain expert consulting activities 
Responsible for resolving technical issues being faced by Automation Engineer Team Members while carrying out Scripting , Test Execution & reporting activities 
Responsible for supporting the Automation Lead in creating and maintaining the Test Plan and Test Strategy as per defined schedule 
Good experience on installation of TOSCA automation tool on several machines 
Good experience in implementing best practices specific to the test planning , Automation scripting , test execution & reporting activities processes 
Good experience in reviewing the Automation deliverables & suggesting improvements if any 
Ability to work independently in Agile / Scrum / Sprint and drive application Automation using TOSCA (Functional / In-Sprint / API / DB / Web / Mobile / Regression / E2E) 
Ability to drive Test Automation Programs for geo. spread teams (NAM, India, Mexico) and own the accountability for successful delivery 
Work with client stakeholders to understand Test Automation requirements and ensure they are transitioned to the geo. spread automation developers 
Client & Program Management with good Exec. Presence to work with client leadership teams 
Excellent Communication" 
